\c 26
\s VaIsraeri, vanogona kurwa, vanoverengwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwe, kuti Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Eriazari mwanakomana Aroni mupristi achiti:
\v 2 Tora uwandu hwese hweungano yese yevana vaIsraeri, kubva pamakore makumi maviri zvichikwira, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, vese vanogona kuenda kuhondo kwaIsraeri.
\v 3 Zvino Mozisi naEriazari mupristi vakataura navo pamapani aMoabhu paJoridhani paJeriko, vachiti:
\v 4 \add Verengai\add* kubva pamakore makumi maviri zvichikwira; Jehovha sezvakaraira Mozisi nevana vaIsraeri, vakabuda kubva panyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 5 Rubheni, dangwe raIsraeri, vanakomana vaRubheni: Hanoki, \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaHanoki; kwaParu, mhuri yeVaParu,
\v 6 kwaHezironi mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaKarimi mhuri yeVaKarimi.
\v 7 Idzi imhuri dzeVaRubheni; nevakaverengwa kwavari vaiva zvuru makumi mana nezvitatu nemazana manomwe nemakumi matatu.
\v 8 Nevanakomana vaParu: Eriabhu;
\v 9 nevanakomana vaEriabhu, Nemueri naDhatani naAbhiramu. Ndivo Dhatani naAbhiramu vakange vakadanwa neungano, vakapikisa Mozisi naAroni paboka raKora, pavakapikisa Jehovha,
\v 10 nyika ndokushamisa muromo wayo, ndokuvamedza pamwe naKora pakafa boka iro; iyo nguva moto yawakaparadza varume mazana maviri nemakumi mashanu, ivo ndokuva chiratidzo.
\v 11 Asi vanakomana VaKora havana kufa.
\p
\v 12 Vanakomana vaSimioni zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: KwaNemueri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaNemueri, kwaJamini mhuri yeVaJamini, kwaJakini mhuri yeVaJakini;
\v 13 kwaZera mhuri yeVaZera; kwaShauri mhuri yeVaShauri.
\v 14 Idzi imhuri dzeVaSimioni, zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri nemazana maviri.
\p
\v 15 Vanakomana vaGadhi zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: KwaZefoni \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaZefoni; kwaHagi mhuri yeVaHagi; kwaShuni mhuri yeVaShuni;
\v 16 kwaZini mhuri yeVaZini; kwaEri mhuri yeVaEri;
\v 17 kwaArodhi mhuri yeVaArodhi; kwaAreri mhuru yeVaAreri.
\v 18 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaGadhi; avo vakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi mana nemazana mashanu.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaJudha: Eri naOnani; Eri naOnani ndokufira munyika yeKenani.
\v 20 Zvino vanakomana vaJudha zvichitevera mhuri dzavo ndeava: KwaShera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShera; kwaPerezi mhuri yeVaPerezi; kwaZera mhuri yeVaZera.
\v 21 Zvino vanakomana VaPerezi ndeava: KwaHezironi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaHamuri mhuri yeVaHamuri.
\v 22 Idzi imhuri dzaJudha; zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi manomwe nezvitanhatu nemazana mashanu.
\p
\v 23 Vanakomana vaIsaskari zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: Tora \add we\add*mhuri yeVaTora; kwaPuwa \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaPuwa;
\v 24 kwaJashubhi mhuri yeVaJashubhi, kwaShimironi mhuri yeVaShimironi.
\v 25 Idzi imhuri dzaIsaskari zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi matanhatu nezvina nemazana matatu.
\p
\v 26 Vanakomana vaZebhuruni zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: KwaSeredhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaSeredhi; kwaaEroni mhuri yeVaEroni; kwaJahareeri mhuri yeVaJahareeri.
\v 27 Idzi imhuri dzeVaZebhuruni; vakaverengwa kwavari; zvuru makumi matanhatu nemazana mashanu.
\p
\v 28 Ava vanakomana vaJosefa zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: Manase naEfuremu.
\v 29 Vanakomana vaManase: KwaMakiri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaMakiri. Zvino Makiri wakabereka Giriyadhi; kwaGiriyadhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaGiriyadhi.
\v 30 Ava vanakomana vaGiriyadhi: Jezeri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJezeri; kwaHereki mhuri yeVaHereki;
\v 31 uye \add kwa\add*Asirieri mhuri yeVaAsirieri; ne\add kwa\add*Shekemu mhuri yeVaShekemu;
\v 32 uye \add kwa\add*Shemidha mhuri yeVaShemidha; ne\add kwa\add*Heferi mhuri yeVaHeferi.
\p
\v 33 Zvino Zerofehadhi mwanakomana waHeferi wakange asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana; uye mazita evanasikana vaZerofehadhi \add aiva\add* Makira, naNowa, Hogira, Mirika, naTiriza.
\v 34 Idzi imhuri dzaManase; uye vakaverengwa vavo zvuru makumi mashanu nezviviri nemazana manomwe.
\p
\v 35 Ava vanakomana vaEfuremu zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: KwaShutera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShutera; kwaBhekeri mhuri yeVaBhekeri, kwaTahani, mhuri yeVaTahani.
\v 36 Ava vanakomana vaShutera: kwaErani \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaErani.
\p
\v 37 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi matatu nezviviri nemazana mashanu. Ava vanakomana vaJosefa zvichitevera mhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 38 Vanakomana vaBhenjamini zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaBhera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaBhera; kwaAshibheri mhuri yeVaAshibheri; kwaAhirami mhuri yeVaAhirami;
\v 39 kwaShefufami mhuri yeVaShufami; kwaHufami mhuri yeVaHufami.
\v 40 Zvino vanakomana vaBhera vaiva Aridhi naNamani; \add kwaAridhi\add* mhuri yeVaAridhi; \add kwa\add*Namani mhuri yeVaNamani.
\v 41 Ava vanakomana vaBhenjamini, zvichitevera mhuri dzavo uye vakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi mana nezvishanu nemazana matanhatu.
\p
\v 42 Ava vanakomana vaDhani zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaShuhami kwakabva mhuri yeVaShuhami. Idzi imhuri dzaDhani, nedzimba dzavo.
\v 43 Mhuri dzese dzevaShuhami zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi matanhatu nezvina nemazana mana.
\p
\v 44 Vanakomana vaAsheri zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaJimina \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJimina; kwaIshivhi mhuri yeVaIshivhi; kwaBheria mhuri yeVaBheria.
\v 45 Kuvanakomana vaBheria: kwaHebheri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHebheri; kwaMakieri mhuri yeVaMakieri.
\v 46 Zvino zita remwanasikana waAsheri \add raiva\add* Sera.
\v 47 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaAsheri zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi mashanu nezvitanhatu nemazana mana.
\p
\v 48 Vanakomana vaNafutari zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaJazeeri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJazeri; kwaGuni mhuri yeVaGuni;
\v 49 kwaJezeri mhuri yeVaJezeri; kwaShiremi mhuri yeVaShiremi.
\v 50 Idzi imhuri dzaNafutari zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi mana nezvishanu nemazana mana.
\p
\v 51 Ava ndevakaverengwa vevana vaIsraeri; zvuru mazana matanhatu nechiuru chimwe nemazana manomwe nemakumi matatu.
\p
\v 52 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 53 Kune ava nyika ichagoverwa kuva nhaka zvichienderana neuwandu hwemazita.
\v 54 Kuvazhinji uchapa nhaka yakawedzerwa uye kuvashoma uchapa nhaka shoma; kune umwe neumwe kuchapiwa nhaka yake zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vake.
\v 55 Zvakadaro nyika ichagoverwa nemujenya; zvichienderana nemazita endudzi dzemadzibaba avo vachagara nhaka.
\v 56 Zvichienderana nemujenya nhaka yawo ichatsaurwa pakati pevazhinji nevashoma.
\p
\v 57 Zvino ava \add nde\add*vakaverengwa veVaRevhi zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaGerishoni \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaGerishoni; kwaKohati mhuri yeVaKohati; kwaMerari mhuri yeVaMerari.
\v 58 Idzi imhuri dzeVaRevhi: Mhuri yeVaRibhini, mhuri yeVaHebhuroni, mhuri yeVaMahiri, mhuri yeVaMushi, mhuri yeVaKora. Kohati ndokubereka Amuramu.
\v 59 Zvino zita remukadzi waAmuramu raiva Jokebhedhi mwanasikana waRevhi, waakaberekera Revhi muEgipita; ndokuberekera Amuramu Aroni naMozisi naMiriami hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 60 Zvino kuna Aroni kwakaberekerwa Nadhabhi naAbhihu naEriazari naItamari.
\v 61 Zvino Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa pavakapa moto usingazikanwi pamberi paJehovha.
\v 62 Zvino avo vakaverengwa vavo vaiva zvuru makumi maviri nezvitatu, vanhurume vese kubva pane ane mwedzi zvichikwira; nokuti havana kuverengwa pakati pevana vaIsraeri, nokuti havana kupiwa nhaka pakati pevana vaIsraeri.
\p
\v 63 Ava ndevakaverengwa naMozisi naEriazari mupristi, vavakaverenga vana vaIsraeri pamapani aMoabhu, paJoridhani paJeriko.
\v 64 Asi pakati peava hapana murume wavo Mozisi naAroni mupristi wavakaverenga pavakaverenga vana vaIsraeri murenje reSinai.
\v 65 Nokuti Jehovha wakange ati pamusoro pavo: Zvirokwazvo vachafira murenje. Zvino hakuna kusara munhu kwavari kunze kwaKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune, naJoshua, mwanakomana waNuni.